  "snippet": "Registreer je voor My Eneco Hallo, Je ontvangt deze mail omdat je het wachtwoord van je My Eneco account opnieuw wilt instellen. Maar we vinden geen My Eneco account voor dit e-mailadres. Heb je nog",
  "subject": "Je account is niet gekend op My Eneco",
  "from": "Eneco klantendienst <welcome@eneco.be>",
  "date": "Thu, 12 Mar 2026 11:19:11 +0000 (UTC)",
  "body": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\r\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\r\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0; user-scalable=no;\">\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=9; IE=8; IE=7; IE=EDGE\" />\r\n    <title>Registreer je voor My Eneco</title>\r\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n        /* Some resets and issue fixes */\r\n        #outlook a {\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        body {\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            -webkit-text:size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ReadMsgBody {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .backgroundTable {\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .table-wrapper {\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            line-height: 100% !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        table {\r\n            border-collapse: collapse;\r\n            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;\r\n            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n            table td {\r\n                border-collapse: collapse;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass * {\r\n            line-height: 115%;\r\n        }\r\n        /* End reset */\r\n        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {\r\n            .table-full {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-padding-outer {\r\n                padding-left: 0px !important;\r\n                padding-right: 0px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-padding-inner {\r\n                padding-left: 25px !important;\r\n                padding-right: 25px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-hide {\r\n                display: none !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-title {\r\n                font-size: 30px !important;\r\n                line-height: 36px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .img-full {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n                height: auto !important;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"padding:0; margin:0; background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n\r\n    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin:0; padding:0;\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                <!-- TITLE -->\r\n                <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:15px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-title\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:40px; line-height:46px; color:#09354B; font-weight:bold;\">Registreer je voor My Eneco</td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <!-- TITLE -->\r\n\r\n                <!-- INTRO -->\r\n                <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:10px 40px;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000; padding-bottom:20px;\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td>\r\n                                                    Hallo,<br /><br />\r\n                                                    Je ontvangt deze mail omdat je het wachtwoord van je My Eneco account opnieuw wilt instellen. Maar we vinden geen My Eneco account voor dit e-mailadres.<br />\r\n                                                    <br /><br />\r\n                                                    Heb je nog geen account? Registreer dan via deze <a href=\"https://account.eneco.be/nl/register?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#72bdce;\">link</a> met je klantnummer en familienaam.\r\n                                                    <br /><br />\r\n                                                    Of misschien heb je wel al een account, maar met een ander e-mailadres? Via deze <a href=\"https://account.eneco.be/nl/email/recover?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#72bdce;\">link</a> kan je het e-mailadres van jouw account opvragen.\r\n                                                </td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td style=\"padding-top: 15px;\">\r\n                                                    <b>Inloggen met itsme<sup>®</sup></b><br />\r\n                                                    Wist je dat je nu ook op My Eneco kan <b>inloggen</b> met <b>itsme<sup>®</sup></b>?\r\n                                                    <br />Op My Eneco kan je bij 'Mijn gegevens' je makkelijk verbinden met itsme<sup>®</sup>. Op die manier kan je op elk moment en overal inloggen op My Eneco en hoef je het e-mailadres waarmee je bent gekoppeld niet meer op te vragen.\r\n                                                </td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <!-- INTRO -->\r\n                <!-- HELP -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:20px 40px 50px 40px;\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:24px; line-height:30px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; padding-bottom:10px;\">We zijn er voor jou</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000;\">\r\n                                    Heb je nog vragen? Bel gerust iedere werkdag tussen 8 en 18 uur naar <strong>015 25 66 66</strong> of surf naar ons\r\n                                    <a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/formulieren/contact/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#D21242; text-decoration:underline;\">contactformulier</a>.\r\n                                    <br /><br />Met vriendelijke groeten,<br />\r\n                                    <strong>Het Eneco-team</strong>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- HELP -->\r\n<!-- CONTACT -->\r\n<table width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#F3F3F3\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#F3F3F3\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                                    <table width=\"100%\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> My Eneco</a></td>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/contact?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> Veelgestelde vragen</a></td>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/contact?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> Klantendienst</a></td>\r\n                                        </tr>\r\n                                    </table>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- CONTACT -->\r\n<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:0 40px;\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:10px; line-height:16px; color:#7F7F7F;\">Eneco Belgium nv – Battelsesteenweg 455i – 2800 Mechelen – btw BE 0683.948.879<br />&copy; Eneco \r\n                                    - <a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/Optin/EditOptin?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#626262; text-decoration:underline;\">Bepaal zelf hoeveel en waarover je van ons wil horen. Power to the people!</a>\r\n                                    – <a href=\"https://uat.eneco.be/nl/privacybeleid?utm_medium=email&utm_source=unknownaccountmail&utm_campaign=myregistration\" style=\"color:#7F7F7F; text-decoration:underline;\">Privacybeleid</a></td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n<!-- START GMAIL FIX -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-hide\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#F6F6F6; line-height:1px; height:1px; min-width:600px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.eneco.be/images/mails/Web/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"1\" style=\"max-height:1px; min-height:1px; display:block; width:600px; min-width:600px;\" /></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- END GMAIL FIX -->\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n",
